\li1 
\v 34 The son of Jonathan: 
\b
\li2 Merib-baal,\f + \fr 8:34 \ft Merib-baal is also called Mephibosheth; see 2 Samuel 4:4.\f* and Merib-baal was the father of Micah.\f + \fr 8:34 \ft Micah is a variant of Mica; see 2 Samuel 9:12.\f* 
\b
\li1 
\v 35 The sons of Micah: 
\b
